query:
SELECT id, name, email, 
  CASE WHEN googleCalendarAccessToken IS NOT NULL THEN 'YES' ELSE 'NO' END as hasCalendarToken,
  CASE WHEN googleCalendarRefreshToken IS NOT NULL THEN 'YES' ELSE 'NO' END as hasRefreshToken,
  googleCalendarTokenExpiry
FROM users 
WHERE email = 'angelaneason@gmail.com'
LIMIT 1;
